                <fr:display-uri>idem-comm-B7DD</fr:display-uri>
                <fr:route>/idem-comm-B7DD/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="t-conservative maps are not injective">t-conservative maps are not injective</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Remark</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
  Note that t-conservative maps are not necessarily <html:em>injective</html:em>. The following is such an example:
  
  
  <html:figure><fr:resource hash="2f5a7de2d528d08d09ba8bdb9ca1463b"><fr:resource-content><html:img src="/2f5a7de2d528d08d09ba8bdb9ca1463b.svg" /></fr:resource-content><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="preamble"><![CDATA[\usepackage {tikz-cd}\usepackage {quiver}]]></fr:resource-source><fr:resource-source type="latex" part="body"><![CDATA[
    \begin {tikzcd}
      \bullet  \ar [r, dashed] & \bullet  \\
      \bullet  \ar [u] \ar [dr, dashed] & \\ 
      \bullet  \ar [u] \ar [r, dashed] & \bullet  \ar [uu]
    \end {tikzcd}
  ]]></fr:resource-source></fr:resource></html:figure></html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
